section.div: I build projects with React, Tailwind, and Vite and I am currently exploring NextJS. I also worked on backend with NodeJS, Express & Spring Boot.

div.title: Algorithms are self-contained sequences that carry out a variety of tasks.
React is an open source JavaScript library used for designing user interfaces.
Amazon Web Services provides on-demand cloud computing platforms on a subscription basis.
Node.js is a tool for executing JavaScript in a variety of environments.
An awesome list is a list of awesome things curated by the community.
TypeScript is a typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript.
MongoDB is an open source NoSQL document-oriented database.
Hacktoberfest is a month-long celebration of open source projects, their maintainers, and the entire community of contributors.
A web application is any computer program that performs a specific function by using a web browser as its client.
ChatGPT is a chatbot built on top of OpenAI's GPT-3 family of large language models.
Next.js is an open source React front-end development web framework.
ChatGPT API is a RESTful API that provides a simple interface to interact with OpenAI's GPT-3 and GPT-Neo language models.
